title: Extreme Limits aka Crash Point Zero (MKV)
description:
R | 1h 33min | Action, Adventure | March 23rd 2001



A scientist recovers a powerful weapon created by inventor Nicola Tesla in the early twentieth century. Now, the plane carrying the device and a disparate group of passengers crashes in the Canadian mountains. The battle to survive begins.


Director: Jim Wynorski (as Jay Andrews)

Writer: Steve Latshaw

Stars: Treat Williams, Hannes Jaenicke, Gary Hudson



English audio, English and Spanish subtitles.

NTSC-1
